org.wonderly.util.jini
Class LookupEnvList

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

          java.util.ArrayList<LookupEnv>
              org.wonderly.util.jini.LookupEnvList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<LookupEnv>, Collection<LookupEnv>, List<LookupEnv>, RandomAccess
public class LookupEnvList
extends ArrayList<LookupEnv>

This class provides a mechanism for loading a complete LookupEnv array of data from an XML file. The format of the XML file is define as follows. 

 <lookupEnvs>
        <lookupEnv
                        codebase="http://eqwe.com:8080/srv-dl.jar"
                        name="Remote Services">
                <group name="xyzzy"/>
                <locator name="host" port="port"/>
                <bindas host="host"/>
                <template serviceid="840329489304312-392103210232">
                        <class name="com.xxxxxx"/>
                        <entry class="com.foo.bar.entry.MyMagicEntry">
                                <int val="99"/>
                                <string val="yywewq"/>
                                <float val="2321.22"/>
                                <double val="2932139213.0232"/>
                        </entry>
                </template>
        </lookupEnv>
</lookupEnvs>
